接口 CompilationUnit

  • 所有已知实现类:
    Interface, TopLevelClass, TopLevelEnumeration

    public interface CompilationUnit
    This interface describes methods common to all Java compilation units (Java classes, interfaces, and enums).
    作者:
    Jeff Butler
